<?xml version="1.0"?><eml:eml xmlns:eml="eml://ecoinformatics.org/eml-2.0.1" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" packageId="lpju.3.4" scope="system" system="knb" xsi:schemaLocation="eml://ecoinformatics.org/eml-2.0.1 eml.xsd"><dataset scope="document"><title>依RAPD標誌推論台灣杉屬之遺傳多樣性</title><creator id="1165919627140" scope="document"><individualName><salutation>助理研究員</salutation><givenName>麗萍</givenName><surName>朱</surName></individualName><organizationName>行政院農業委員會林業試驗所</organizationName><positionName>森林生物組</positionName><address scope="document"><deliveryPoint>南海路53號</deliveryPoint><deliveryPoint>中正區</deliveryPoint><city>Taipei</city><postalCode>10066</postalCode><country>Taiwan</country></address><phone phonetype="voice">886-2-23039978-2802</phone><phone phonetype="fax">886-2-23076220</phone><electronicMailAddress>lpju@tfri.gov.tw</electronicMailAddress></creator><abstract><para>本研究醫逢機擴大多型性(RAPD)來進行台灣杉屬植物之遺傳變異分析：禿杉材料採自中國大陸福建屏南、貴州雷公山以及雲南騰衝；台灣杉的材料則來自六龜研究中心20林班台灣杉單親後裔試驗林木之雪山、望鄉及關山三個族群之種源，並以柳杉作為群外對照。RAPD電泳以POPGENE套裝軟體進行族群遺傳變異之相關分析，結果顯示台灣杉之關山和望鄉地區族群的相似性指數最高，為0.9645，雪山和望鄉地區之相似性指數次之；而中國大陸地區之禿杉族群則以貴州和雲南之族群相關係數0.9228最高，福建和貴州地區族群之0.9050次之。依據樹狀圖分析，禿杉與台灣杉之類群雖可以清楚的區分兩個類群，但兩類群之聯結點僅在11.1，顯見兩類群有非常大之相似性。中國大陸禿杉的遺傳歧異度為0.1744低於台灣杉之0.2271，兩者總歧異度為0.2709，數值偏低。本研究用UPGMA樹枝狀圖得出兩類群間之遺傳相似度為0.8890，仍在種內族群間內之變異範圍，應可列於同一種群之下，但兩者之間的基因流Nm值低於1，為0.7533，顯示禿杉和台灣杉之間有基因交流的障礙存在，而兩者亦顯示禿杉和台灣杉之仍具有可資區別之定量及定性形態特徵。</para></abstract><keywordSet><keyword>台灣杉</keyword><keyword>禿杉</keyword><keyword>RAPD</keyword><keyword>遺傳變異</keyword></keywordSet><intellectualRights><para>引用資料請來信告知原作者</para></intellectualRights><coverage scope="document"><geographicCoverage scope="document"><geographicDescription>Shuei-shan</geographicDescription><boundingCoordinates><westBoundingCoordinate>121.25</westBoundingCoordinate><eastBoundingCoordinate>121.25</eastBoundingCoordinate><northBoundingCoordinate>24.375</northBoundingCoordinate><southBoundingCoordinate>24.375</southBoundingCoordinate></boundingCoordinates></geographicCoverage><geographicCoverage scope="document"><geographicDescription>Wang-hsiang</geographicDescription><boundingCoordinates><westBoundingCoordinate>121.0</westBoundingCoordinate><eastBoundingCoordinate>121.0</eastBoundingCoordinate><northBoundingCoordinate>23.625</northBoundingCoordinate><southBoundingCoordinate>23.625</southBoundingCoordinate></boundingCoordinates></geographicCoverage><geographicCoverage scope="document"><geographicDescription>Guan-shan</geographicDescription><boundingCoordinates><westBoundingCoordinate>121.0</westBoundingCoordinate><eastBoundingCoordinate>121.0</eastBoundingCoordinate><northBoundingCoordinate>23.125</northBoundingCoordinate><southBoundingCoordinate>23.125</southBoundingCoordinate></boundingCoordinates></geographicCoverage><geographicCoverage scope="document"><geographicDescription>Pin-nan</geographicDescription><boundingCoordinates><westBoundingCoordinate>118.875</westBoundingCoordinate><eastBoundingCoordinate>118.875</eastBoundingCoordinate><northBoundingCoordinate>27.0</northBoundingCoordinate><southBoundingCoordinate>27.0</southBoundingCoordinate></boundingCoordinates></geographicCoverage><geographicCoverage scope="document"><geographicDescription>Rei-gong-shan</geographicDescription><boundingCoordinates><westBoundingCoordinate>108.125</westBoundingCoordinate><eastBoundingCoordinate>108.125</eastBoundingCoordinate><northBoundingCoordinate>25.375</northBoundingCoordinate><southBoundingCoordinate>25.375</southBoundingCoordinate></boundingCoordinates></geographicCoverage><geographicCoverage scope="document"><geographicDescription>Tern-chong</geographicDescription><boundingCoordinates><westBoundingCoordinate>100.125</westBoundingCoordinate><eastBoundingCoordinate>100.125</eastBoundingCoordinate><northBoundingCoordinate>25.125</northBoundingCoordinate><southBoundingCoordinate>25.125</southBoundingCoordinate></boundingCoordinates></geographicCoverage><temporalCoverage scope="document"><singleDateTime><calendarDate>2006</calendarDate></singleDateTime></temporalCoverage><taxonomicCoverage scope="document"><taxonomicClassification><taxonRankName>Family</taxonRankName><taxonRankValue>Taxodiaceae</taxonRankValue><commonName>杉科</commonName><taxonomicClassification><taxonRankName>Genus</taxonRankName><taxonRankValue>Taiwania</taxonRankValue><commonName>台灣杉屬</commonName><taxonomicClassification><taxonRankName>Species</taxonRankName><taxonRankValue>cryptomerioides</taxonRankValue><commonName>台灣杉</commonName></taxonomicClassification></taxonomicClassification></taxonomicClassification><taxonomicClassification><taxonRankName>Family</taxonRankName><taxonRankValue>Taxodiaceae</taxonRankValue><commonName>杉科</commonName><taxonomicClassification><taxonRankName>Genus</taxonRankName><taxonRankValue>Taiwania</taxonRankValue><commonName>台灣杉屬</commonName><taxonomicClassification><taxonRankName>Species</taxonRankName><taxonRankValue>flousiana</taxonRankValue><commonName>禿杉</commonName></taxonomicClassification></taxonomicClassification></taxonomicClassification></taxonomicCoverage></coverage><contact scope="document"><references>1165919627140</references></contact><methods><methodStep><description><section><title>野外採樣</title><para>本試驗以台灣杉屬之禿杉(Taiwania jlousiana Gaussen)及台灣杉(Taiwania cryptomerioides Hay.)兩個目前被認定的兩個分類群之代表族群為採樣對象。禿杉的天然分布有3個區塊：1.緬甸北部及雲南境內，2.湖北、四川及貴州交界處，3.近7-8年間發現的福建地區群落。本研究禿杉材料採自雲南騰衝(代表雲南族群或&quot;雲南亞杉&quot;)、貴州省雷公山(代表貴州、湖北、四川族群或禿杉)及褔建省南屏縣(代表褔建地區的族群)。台灣地區的台灣杉取自林業試驗所六龜分所20林班台灣杉單親後裔試驗14年生之立木，包含台灣杉3個種源(雪山、望鄉、關山)15家系。本研究以柳杉為群外對照，從96個單株樣木採集一年生枝葉5cm長數段，立即裝於液態氮之中，運回實驗室。</para></section></description></methodStep><methodStep><description><section><title>試驗方法1.葉片DNA萃取及定量</title><para>每株樣木新鮮幼嫩葉片100 mg於液態氮中磨碎，萃取方法採用修改自Junghans and Metzalaff(1990)的方法。萃取出的DNA稀釋10倍後，以分光光度計測定濃度，再將所有DNA樣品所調整為25 ng/ul工作濃度備用。</para><para>Reference:</para><para>Junghans, H. and M. Metzalaff. 1990. A simple and rapid method for the preparation of total DNA. Bio Techniques 8: 176.</para></section></description></methodStep><methodStep><description><section><title>試驗方法2.PCR反應</title><para>進行PCR反應時，反應體積為20uL。其內含物質濃度為10 mM TrisHCl(pH 8.3)，50 mM KCl; 0.1 mg/mL gelatin; 1.5 mM MgCl2; 100 uM dNTP(包含dATP、dTTP、dCTP、dGTP); 0.2 uM引子(引子序列詳見Table)。</para><para>將配好之DNA混合液在Thermal cycler中進行反應。反應管中加入相等體積之矽油(silicon oil)，避免高溫所造成沸騰蒸發的影響。反應循環設定94°C 2 min，1個循環(預熱處理); 95°C 1 min(雙股DNA轉為單股)、37°C 1 min(使引子與DNA模板聯結)、72°C 2 min(讓Taq作用複製DNA片段)，重複40個循環; 72°C 10 min(讓Taq充分作用，完整複製DNA片段)，反應結束溫度設定在4°C。</para></section></description><instrumentation>參試的引子有OPY-02、OPY-03、OPY-04、OPY-05、OPY-06、OPY-08、OPY-10、OPY-13、OPY-15、OPZ-01、OPZ-02、OPZ-04、OPZ-05、OPZ-09、OPZ-13、OPZ-14、 OPZ-17、OPZ-18、OPZ-20等19個引子，有可供判別的條帶者有OPY-02、OPY-04、OPY-05、OPY-08、OPY-10、OPZ-13、OPZ-14、 OPZ-17、0PZ-18共9個引子。</instrumentation></methodStep><methodStep><description><section><title>試驗方法3.電泳操作</title><para>吸取PCR產物18 uL染劑(loading dye: 15% Ficoll, 0.25% Bromophenol Blue, 0.25% Xylene cyanole FF)混合以溶於0.5 X TBE (0.08 M Triz-base, 0.08 M Boric acid, 0.1 M EDTA(pH8.0))緩衝液之1.6%洋菜膠進行電泳。電泳緩衝液為0.5 X TBE緩衝液，並於膠片兩側加入DNA ladder marker 2 uL (100bp, 12 bands: 100-1200 bp; Bio Lab)、ddH2O 14 uL及3 uL染劑混合液，通電壓100 V.約2.5 hrs，待染劑接近膠體末端時結束電泳。電泳後將膠體置入0.5 ul/mL EtBr中染色約30 mins後置於UV光源下拍照，以供判識之用。</para></section></description></methodStep><methodStep><description><section><title>試驗方法4.資料分析</title><para>為避免缺失，減少誤差，同一樣本均進行3重複。將每一重複中出現之條帶加以判定，條帶之亮度超過ladder marker的1/2者並於3 重複中出現超過2重複者予以採計，將出現之排出0、1矩陣進行歧異度分析。樣本間之歧異度則以POPGENE套裝軟體進行族群遺傳變異之相關分析統計，並以AMOVA程式進行築巢分析。</para></section></description></methodStep><methodStep><description><section><title>統計分析1.以POPGENE套裝軟體進行族群遺傳變異之相關分析統計</title><para>以POPGENE套裝軟體(Nei, 1973, 1978)發表的公式計算標準遺傳距離D(Nei, 1972, 1975)，D=-ln logeI(Nei, 1987)。並依照McDermott and Mc Donald(1993)的公式計算Nm基因流(Gene flow)Nm(=0.5(l-Gst)/Gst)。Nei(1977)把Gst稱作&quot;基因分化係數&quot;(Coefficient of gene differentiation)Gst的值介於1到0之間，值越大，各族群間的基因分化相對量越大。</para><para>Reference:</para><para>McDermott, J. M., B. A. McDonald. 1993. Gene flow in plant pathosystems. Ann. Rev. Phytopathol. 31: 353-373.</para><para>Nei, M. 1972. Genetic distance between populations. Am. Math. Stat. 20: 91-94.</para><para>Nei, M. 1973. Analysis of gene diversity in subdivided populations. Proc. Natl. Acad. Sci. USA. 70: 3321-3323.</para><para>Nei, M. 1977. F-statistics and analysis of gene diversity in subdivided populations. Ann. Human. Genet. 41: 225-233.</para><para>Nei, M. 1978. Estimation of average heterozygosity and genetic distance form a small number of individuals. Genetics 89: 583-590.</para></section></description></methodStep><methodStep><description><section><title>統計分析2.群團分析</title><para>利用各種源或各&quot;分類群&quot;的標準遺傳距離矩陣，用配對不加權算術平均值(Sneath and Soka. 1973)(UPGMA, Unweighted pair-group method with arithmetic averaging)進行群團分析，建立樹狀圖，以顯示各種源或各&quot;分類群&quot;親源關係，以探討區域種源或各&quot;分類群&quot;之變異趨勢。</para><para>Reference:</para><para>Snaeth, P. H. A. and R. S. Sokal. 1973. Numerical taxonomy - the principle and practice of numerical classification. San Francisco: W. H. Freemam.</para></section></description></methodStep><methodStep><description><section><title>統計分析3.AMOVA(Analysis of Molecular Variance)</title><para>以POPGENE套裝軟體的公式計算遺傳矩陣，以Excoffer et al.(1992)所發展的AMOVA程式進行築巢分析，可以得到地區間、地區內種源間、種源內個體間之變方成分值，及各變方成分所佔總成分的百分比。</para><para>Reference:</para><para>Excoffier, L., P. E. Smouse and J. M. Quattro. 1992. Analysis of molecular variance inferred from metricdistance among DNA haplotypes; Application to human mitochondrial DNA restriction data. Genetics 131: 479-491.</para></section></description></methodStep></methods><access authSystem="knb" order="denyFirst" scope="document"><allow><principal>public</principal><permission>read</permission></allow></access><dataTable id="1166406977613" scope="document"><entityName>Taiwania_2006_Table_1.txt</entityName><entityDescription>Description of materials of Taiwania species used in the study</entityDescription><physical id="1166406976379" scope="document"><objectName>Taiwania_2006_table_1.txt</objectName><size unit="byte">1556</size><dataFormat><textFormat